s With the Trump Administration Are About Mediating Fights Between Corporate Interests</h4></a></div><div class="RelatedPosts-promo" data-reactid="266"><a href="https://theintercept.com/2018/12/18/elizabeth-warren-generic-drugs-bill/" data-reactid="267"><div class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-thumbnail" data-reactid="268"><img height="440" src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/f47fbd54-c3b4-4340-b344-6c4ad0af212c/f47fbd54-c3b4-4340-b344-6c4ad0af212c.bin?auto=compress,format&amp;cs=srgb&amp;dpr=2&amp;h=440&amp;w=440&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces%2Cedges&amp;_=261a5315ffafc83a5b253c1eb61ed2e2" width="440" data-reactid="269"/></div><h4 class="RelatedPosts-promo-link-title" data-reactid="270">Elizabeth Warren Plan Would Allow the Government to Manufacture Its Own Generic Drugs</h4></a></div></div><div class="Post-latest-articles" data-reactid="271"><h4 class="Post-latest-articles-header" data-reactid="272">Latest Stories</h4><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="273"><div data-reactid="274"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="275"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-latin-america-foreign-policy-joe-biden/" data-reactid="276"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="277"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="278"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="279"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="280"><noscript data-reactid="281"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/68115254-b698-4c8d-93e3-ae18f013e128/68115254-b698-4c8d-93e3-ae18f013e128.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=96d69908306e5168585e8e7a6f71fecb" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="282"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="283"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="284"><h4 class="Promo-titl